    parentName: "ul"
  }, "Memories: a person\u2019s memories of their life experience."), mdx("li", {
    parentName: "ul"
  }, "Personality: a person\u2019s recognizable traits and behaviors."), mdx("li", {
    parentName: "ul"
  }, "Biology: a living person with distinctive markers, e.g., Deoxyribo Nucleic Acid (DNA), fingerprints."), mdx("li", {
